divs: Sighting DetailsI did not see these objects until I uploaded them. They appear to be in motion. The smoke you see is cigarette smoke. I noticed someone uploaded a video to youtube taken the same day, except it was dark out and when I paused the video, the objects look exactly what I caught on camera. I took a photo before this one and there were no objects in the photo. The time was 8:19 pm on 24 July 2008. Location was Gladwin, Mi.
